Remove Items from a Collection

Easily remove items that are no longer relevant from a collection.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience, Essentials, Group, Enterprise, Professional, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.
Also available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Performance, Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer Editions.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Enhanced Folder Sharing
Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards

To manage a collection:	
Use CRM Analytics
Open a collection.
Click the action menu next to the item to remove.
Click Remove from Collection. The item is immediately removed from the collection.
